Achievements.Name: Adventure is Out There
Achievements.Description: Defeat the first wave of combat planes.

Achievements.Name: To Paradise Falls
Achievements.Description: Complete the level to start Carl's journey to Paradise Falls.

Achievements.Name: A Bird Named Kevin
Achievements.Description: Find Kevin before Muntz does.

Achievements.Name: Slide and Slither
Achievements.Description: Defeat the giant Anaconda.

Achievements.Name: A Voice In The Mist
Achievements.Description: Find the voice in the mist.

Achievements.Name: Meet the Pack
Achievements.Description: Meet the pack: Alpha, Beta, and Gamma.

Achievements.Description: Avoid being captured by Muntz's dogs.

Achievements.Description: Defeat the giant Crocodile.

Achievements.Name: Adventure is Here
Achievements.Description: Defeat Muntz's canine squadron in the skies above Paradise Falls.

Achievements.Description: Unlock the Bonus Art.

Achievements.Description: Use Russell's Canteen three times.

Achievements.Description: Catch or squash 100 Dio Bugs or Butterflies.

Achievements.Name: Bird Watching Badge
Achievements.Description: Locate Kevin for the first time.

Achievements.Name: Defense Badge
Achievements.Description: Successfully defend against 10 dog ambushes.

Achievements.Name: Fishing Badge
Achievements.Description: Survive against the hungry Piranhas.

Achievements.Description: Make sure to put out your campfire.

Achievements.Name: Hiking Badge
Achievements.Description: Find the picture-perfect view of Paradise Falls.

Achievements.Name: Knot Tying Badge

Achievements.Description: Unlock the extra Multiplayer Combat Maps.

Achievements.Name: Ellie Badge

Achievements.Name: Rare Statue Badge

Achievements.Name: Excavation Badge

Achievements.Name: Beginner's Wings
Achievements.Description: You've accessed the Multiplayer game menu.
